PN,30301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,FA medic who developed hantavirus
OL,7,Fsymptoms on a remote British overseas
OL,8,Fterritory is being cared for in a
OL,9,FLondon hospital, as nine people
OL,10,Fconnected to the MV Hondius cruise
OL,11,Fship outbreak arrive in the UK.
OL,13,FThe group of Britons from the British
OL,14,FSouth Atlantic territories of St
OL,15,FHelena and Ascension Island, who may
OL,16,Fhave been exposed to hantavirus but do
OL,17,Fnot have symptoms, arrived in the UK
OL,18,Fon Sunday evening, authorities have
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,FA medic from Ascension Island was
OL,7,Fbrought to the UK for a "specialist
OL,8,Fassessment" after developing symptoms,
OL,9,Fdescribed as a "highly precautionary
OL,10,Fmeasure" by the UK Health Security
OL,11,FAgency (UKHSA).
OL,13,FHe is being treated at the High
OL,14,FConsequence Infectious Diseases unit
OL,15,Fin Guy's and St Thomas's NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust, the UKHSA added.
OL,18,F"As there is no specialist infectious
OL,19,Fdiseases unit on Ascension Island,"
OL,20,Fthe agency said in an update on
OL,21,FSaturday.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@KO]qD@POUrD@HO]zD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,F"The decision was made to bring them
OL,7,Fto the UK to ensure they receive the
OL,8,Fbest possible support at a HCID unit
OL,9,Fshould they become unwell. The
OL,10,Findividual will undergo further
OL,11,Ftesting and assessment at the unit."
OL,13,FThe group will complete their self-
OL,14,Fisolation in the UK supported by the
OL,15,FNHS's High Consequence Infectious
OL,16,FDiseases network they become unwell,
OL,17,Fthe UKHSA said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,FThey will be taken to Arrowe Park
OL,7,FHospital on the Wirral, the same
OL,8,Ffacility that housed passengers from
OL,9,Fthe MV Hondius.
OL,11,FThe MV Hondius was scheduled to arrive
OL,12,Fin Rotterdam, in the Netherlands, on
OL,13,FMonday morning, having spent the past
OL,14,Fsix days sailing from the Canary
OL,15,FIslands, where passengers were
OL,16,Fescorted off in full protective gear
OL,17,Fand flown to quarantine in over 20
OL,18,Fcountries, including the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,FDr Meera Chand, deputy director at the
OL,7,FUKHSA, said: "UKHSA will continue to
OL,8,Fwork with our partners locally,
OL,9,Fnationally and internationally to
OL,10,Fensure everyone has the necessary
OL,11,Fsupport in place.
OL,13,F"We are undertaking safe repatriation
OL,14,Fof those affected by the outbreak
OL,15,Fwhere appropriate, incorporating
OL,16,Fmedical checks and support, with the
OL,17,Flatest flight arriving tonight.
OL,26,@oD@NOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,F"We are committed to keeping these
OL,7,Fpassengers and the wider population
OL,8,Fsafe and will remain in close contact
OL,9,Fwith them as they complete their self-
OL,10,Fisolation period."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@RO]
