OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,FOn Saturday, one person left Arrowe
OL,7,FPark Hospital to complete their 45-day
OL,8,Fisolation period at home, after a
OL,9,Fclinical and public health assessment
OL,10,Fdeemed it safe for them to do so, the
OL,11,FUKHSA said.
OL,13,FA further six people returned home
OL,14,Ffrom the hospital to continue their
OL,15,Fself-isolation on Thursday last week.
OL,16,FOfficials say both those isolating at
OL,17,Fhome and those who remain in hospital
OL,18,Fare being closely monitored,
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,FThe UKHSA said on Friday evening that
OL,7,Fthree team members of the UK Public
OL,8,FHealth Rapid Support Team (UK-PHRST)
OL,9,Fhad been sent to the UK overseas
OL,10,Fterritories in the South Atlantic in
OL,11,Fresponse to a request for support from
OL,12,Fthe island's government.
OL,14,FThe deployed team includes two
OL,15,Fmicrobiologists, Clara Milroy and
OL,16,FKimberley Steeds, who will support
OL,17,Fwith PCR testing for hantavirus as
OL,18,Fwell as supporting testing to exclude
OL,19,Fother conditions, the UKHSA said on
OL,20,Fits website.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,FThey are joined by infection
OL,7,Fprevention and control expert Anthony
OL,8,FTwyman, who will support Jamestown
OL,9,FGeneral Hospital to prepare and
OL,10,Frespond to any potential cases through
OL,11,Fassessments and training.
OL,13,FThe trio will be on the island for the
OL,14,Fnext eight weeks, according to the
OL,15,Fagency.
OL,17,FThe outbreak on the cruise ship has
OL,18,Fled to at least 11 reported cases
OL,19,Famong passengers, including three
OL,20,Fdeaths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,FAmong those who died were a Dutch
OL,7,Fcouple, who health officials believe
OL,8,Fwere the first exposed to the virus
OL,9,Fwhile visiting South America.
OL,11,FPublic Health Scotland warned on
OL,12,FThursday that a small number of people
OL,13,Fin Scotland have potentially had
OL,14,Fcontact with the virus and that it was
OL,15,Fworking to get in touch with "a small
OL,16,Fnumber of individuals" who could be
OL,17,Faffected.
OL,26,@wD@^OUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,FAfter the ship docks in Rotterdam,
OL,7,Fcrew members who are unable to return
OL,8,Fhome will be quarantined in the
OL,9,FNetherlands, the Dutch health ministry
OL,10,Fsaid last week.
OL,12,FAround two dozen passengers and crew
OL,13,Fare already in quarantine in the
OL,14,FNetherlands, after arriving in the
OL,15,Fcountry on a series of flights over
OL,16,Fthe previous two weeks.
OL,18,FAfter everyone on board has
OL,19,Fdisembarked, the ship will be
OL,20,Fdecontaminated based on Dutch public
OL,21,Fhealth guidelines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,F"Personal protective measures are
OL,7,Fbeing taken to ensure that the
OL,8,Fcleaners do not need to quarantine
OL,9,Fafter the cleaning," the health
OL,10,Fministry said in a letter to the Dutch
OL,11,Fparliament last week.
OL,13,FPublic health officials will inspect
OL,14,Fthe vessel before it is allowed to
OL,15,Fsail again. The hantavirus outbreak
OL,16,Faboard the MV Hondius is the first
OL,17,Fknown case on a cruise ship.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779095182
OL,3,CMedic with hantavirus symptoms being
OL,4,Ctreated in London hospital
OL,6,FThe Dutch company that owns the cruise
OL,7,Fship said it does not foresee any
OL,8,Fchanges to its operations. It has an
OL,9,FArctic cruise setting sail from
OL,10,FKeflavik, Iceland, on May 29.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
